race.comment: MIGHTY SCAR (3) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (30.53) in a Grade 7 at Sandown latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Look for sharp improvement here. DR. GIANNA (1) was impressive last time, posting an effortless 6 lengths win in taking a T3 Grade 7 in 24.77 and a new Best time this course and distance. Expected to feature again. DR. TESSA (8) has a strong record this track and trip including two wins from four starts. Missed the frame latest (30.38) when eighth over 510m at this track in a T3 RSTW. Looks well placed here and among the chances. DR. LOUIS (2) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can turn the form around. Something for the Multiples: DR. GIANNA (1) NEWBROCK TILLY (5)
